reviews.review_text: Was recommended Nash Moving and they did not disappoint. This was my first time using movers, and it was worth the money. They were very efficient, knowledgeable, professional, and friendly. I didn t find any damage in my units, all my items arrived safe and sound
I had a great experience moving my apartment. Nate and his team were very personable and professional, and most importantly, nothing got broken.
Second time my family used Nash Moving Ltd. and again it was 5/5 service. Super friendly, reliable, and generously accommodated my change in plans. Highly recommend.

I cant express how impressed and pleased and happy we were having these guys helping us with our move. Being a realtor I got Nash Moving recommended to me by another realtor. Then I tried them on my clients first and my clients were extremely happy with their service. Then we hired guys for our own move. The guys are working  so hard and so fast and we didnt have a  scratch neither on our furniture nor on any walls. They gave us over 40 large packing bins for packing (returnable), so we didnt need to get any boxes.They wrapped everything and they were working like machines. Yet, their prices are more than reasonable based on quality of their job and the timing. I always recommend Nash Moving to my clients for moving and to my friends and other realtors as well. Next time we move, Nash Moving is our to go company. Way to go guys! You definitely changed the way this industry works! Have you heard of people tipping movers before? Neither did I :)) And we sure did! These guys do amazing job and fully deserve to be tipped. Thats how great they are! We recommend Nash Moving for your next move!

I used Nash Moving and Storage for a rather complex move, involving the sale of 2 homes with different closing dates, all items from one home being placed in storage for 3 months, and then moving out of the second home and moving all items into the new home over a 2 day period.  Nash Moving handled it all with ease, even making a last minute schedule change with no complaint!  The took great care of our belongings, securely packed, wrapped, padded and protected everything, and put it all back together in our new home.  They came ahead of time and quoted me on the move, were very competitive with their pricing, and they charged EXACTLY what they quoted.  I wouldnt hesitate to use Nash Moving & Storage for future moves, and gladly recommend them to anyone that asks.

We have used Nash Moving Ltd. twice now for 2 major moves!  Both times we have been extremely impressed with their level of service & professionalism!  All their employees are super friendly and hard working!  Would definitely use them again in the future as well as recommend them to anybody I now looking for movers!  Thanks again!

We hired Nash Moving for our recent move from Vancouver to Nanaimo. Hands down, this was the best team of movers we have ever worked with (and weve moved quite a few times over the years!). Pricing was reasonable and transparent, communication was easy and clear, and the move itself was smooth and stress-free. Everything was loaded up efficiently and safely, and then delivered quickly and without a scratch. And the moving team was totally fun to just hang out with! I cant recommend them enough.

Im really grateful for Nash Moving Ltds services. They offered me a really good deal for the amount of work done. Nothing was broken during the move, which is a miracle, in my opinion. They are professional and they got it completed in a timely manner (other moving companies, in my experience, waste time sitting around trying to get even more money). This company is a company of integrity, one that can be trusted, and one Id definitely use again in the future.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Great to work wiht you, Tavia!

reviews.review_text: I hired Nash moving to help me move my one bedroom apartment this summer. They were very easy to work with, provided a quote over the phone after a virtual consultation that was super convenient, there were no hidden costs and they were by far the most affordable option I found.  The moving day was smooth, they worked well with the building security on both sides to accommodate covid elevator requirements etc and were friendly as fast. The dissembled and reassembled my large furniture and packed and unpacked my closets in minutes using wardrobe boxes.  Working with Nash saved me a ton of time and stress. I highly recommend, and told me realtor to refer his clients as well because my experience was so positive!

We had Nash Moving do our move during the summer. They came and packed our whole apartment in about 3 hours - that would have taken us probably 2 weeks full time! They were super quick and careful with everything, had a good sense of humor and were  also very respectful. The move was also quick and easy. The boxes they packed everything in make it so much easier to move and unpack too. They left the boxes for 1 month so we could have time to unpack, which was very convenient! Overall, a great experience and would recommend them to anyone!! Service: Moving-related packing
reviews.response_from_owner_text: haha, thanks Andrea. We do love to pack!

reviews.review_text: The team from Nash Moving helped with a move this February and were fantastic! The crew arrived and moved out of a busy downtown apartment, navigating the single elevator booked for the move, and four storage lockers downstairs. The crew moved everything with care, and made sure everything arrived safely and carefully. They even heled to put some awkward furniture into a tricky crawl space in the new home. Cannot recommend them highly enough, efficient, safe, and friendly.

Used Nash moving to move condos and I was very impressed and would highly recommend them! They were professional, on-time and did a fantastic job. I had an issue with getting my treadmill apart in time to move it and they were kind enough to go back for it at the end of the move.  If I ever move I would be using their services for sure!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Glad to hear it, Lynette. WEd love to work with you again!

reviews.review_text: I used Nash moving in September 2020 for a move out to the suburbs and the process so very simple! I got a quote on the phone,  we video called so I could show them around my apartment and all the things that are going to be moved and I got a quote the very next day.  I accepted the quote and they showed up on the date. the move was seamless! they were very careful with all my items and wrapped necessary ones.  They disassembled my bed frame and reassembled.  I couldnt have asked for a more stress free moving day! the price is very fair and there were no extra charges beyond the quote.  Thank you again, I 100% recommended Nash Moving!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: We 100% recommend you as great customer, Lindsay!

reviews.review_text: Nash Moving was recommended by a friend, and they didn t disappoint. The frog boxes made things so much easier, and the crew was professional, did a great job within the expected time, and were cool people. No surprises, and we paid the guaranteed quote which was fair value for the job done. I hope I never have to move again, but if I do I ll use Nash!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: WEre here whenever you need us, Roland! lol!

reviews.review_text: I could not be more happy and pleased in every way with the service provided by Nash Moving Ltd. They were everything you could hope for and more. A friend of mine heard about their expertise and professionalism and mentioned them to me. Everything was shrink-wrapped and moved very carefully asking me where I wanted each piece upon arrival. One doesnt expect a mover to show personal kindness and thoughtfulness if you are having a particularly bad day. It was due to these unforeseen circumstances that I had to phone Nate and ask if he could possibly move more items on a day during which he had hoped to just relax. Nate and company are the best and most likeable movers I have ever used and Im now a senior! Nate is not only more than obliging he is compassionate too. It is perhaps this part of his personality that is as valuable as his moving expertise. I have never been in even a remotely similar personal situation before but Nates kindness made such a difference in my day. Thank you so very much Nate! Just in case any readers might think this is a marriage separation or problem within causing my grief please know that this was not the situation. I will be recommending Nash Moving Ltd. to everyone I know when they need a professional, reliable mover in every way! They do not come any better!

The best moving experience I have ever had. They are amazing! Needed to move in a hurry and Nash moving made it happen. Friendly professional reasonably priced and stress free. Nate even took apart and put my bed back together for me!  I highly recommend Nash moving!

Ive had a fair number of poor experiences with movers in the past, so Im ecstatic to have found a quality team like Nash Movers to help us move from Vancouver to Port Moody. (And will definitely be a return customer when we move in the future.) These guys know their business. More importantly, they demonstrate a real concern for excellent service throughout the experience. From start to finish, they were both professional and friendly, and they showed great care with our possessions and about timing. When youre buying a new home, in particular, the last thing you want is to have to worry about the movers. Nash earned my confidence and kept it from start to finish.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Wow thanks you so much, Colin!

reviews.review_text: I cannot say enough about Nash Moving Ltd. We were recommended to them about 5 years ago from a friend when we were moving, they went above and beyond and were so professional, respectful of our belongings and super quick and efficient! We just recently moved again last month and there was no question who we would use for moving day. We reccomend them to everyone we know and their experience has always been the same. My Brother and Sister in law are using them this weekend for a move and they messaged me today to just say how great they have been with their communication thus far. Thanks again Aaron and the rest of the Team at Nash Moving we will forever spread the word of how great of a service you provide.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you so much for trusting us with your family!

reviews.review_text: This was the first time I used NASH and from now on it will be the only company I ever use. The guys were on time and so friendly and professional. They were careful with everything even my antique furniture(+100 years).  My husband packs very heavy and there were no complaints from the guys. They completed the move on time and left no mess. Next time I may even get them to pack for us. Very reasonably priced too, exactly as quoted.

I moved yesterday and I wanted to share my experience. Overall I had a great experience and I am so happy that I ve decided to use Nash movers. They provide & deliver boxes that makes it super easy to pack. My quote was done on a video call and it took less than 5 minutes. They came in time and where very professional. Super fast and efficient (I had used other movers before that took double the time to do the same job). They also picked up the boxes within one day of me texting them. I am very again very happy and totally recommend them :)
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you Romina! It was our pleasure!

reviews.review_text: I had an amazing experience with Nash Moving.  Nate was professional, responsive and went above and beyond!  Their prices are competitive and I highly recommend this company for anyones moving needs.  Thank you Nate!  Susan Fuller

I have used Nash Moving for my last 3 moves. They are quick and very professional! I also recommend getting the reusable boxes as part of your package. They get dropped off before your move and picked up after you are done unpacking-super convenient!

Weve had a wonderful experience moving with Nash.  The quote was transparent, crew were friendly and they move stuff real quick.  Those boxes they provided were awesome and we didnt have anything damaged after the move.  Highly recommended!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Great to be of service to you!

reviews.review_text: I m so happy that I decided to go with this moving company. They were fantastic to work with and moved all of my furniture carefully and efficiently. About two weeks prior they dropped off 75 bins that I would never move without again. It saved me so much time and money not having to build and pack up boxes. They wrapped our fragile furniture and unwrapped it at the new house. They were careful and the move went smoothly. Communication was top notch. I can t say enough good things! I would never use another company. Thanks guys!

The Team at Nash are the best. From the quote, to the reusable boxes they let us borrow, to everything on the day, these guys were amazing to work with. Their price was locked in from the first quote and it was so great to have the peace of mind of no hidden charges.    These guys are amazing! If we ever do another local move we will use them again for sure!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Great to work with you, Stephanie!

reviews.review_text: What a wonderful moving experience! Nate and the crew took excellent care of me from dropping off my boxes to picking them up .  My move was a bit tricky due to complications with my condo parking but Nate went the extra mile and went overtime to make sure everything was perfect.  The movers are so professional and personable and I will recommend them to everyone.  All my belongings arrived in excellent condition and was delivered with a great attitude.  Thank you thank you thank you.

I have had bad experiences in the past with movers but Nash Moving Ltd squashed all my fear.  Amazing customer services before and after!!  They made my move 150% stress free.  They even got rid of my junk!  I ve recommended to my friends who also rave about their services! I am not planning to move anytime soon but I guarantee when I do, they are the first call in my list!!!

My friend had referred me to this company.  I had not moved in many years and this was a big and emotional move for me.  They were extremely professional and very compassionate, hard working and kind.  I needed help setting up a couple of items cause I lost my tool bit and they were so helpful.  They moved my items with care and protection and nothing got damaged.  They took extreme care in handling items that were delicate. I highly recommend Nash Moving and if I ever need to move again, I will only use them.  They are absolutely amazing.

Nash Moving just moved us from Surrey BC to West Kelowna. They were fantastic. The quote was fair, they gave us tons of boxes and got everything out and in in excellent time. They are a great to work with. Id recommend them to anyone who needs a moving service.
Nate and team are a great bunch of guys!  Very polite, on budget, no damage to any of our prized possessions.  Not that we are moving again any time but would definitely use Nash again!

These guys are phenomenal... I ve moved nearly a dozen times in the last 10 years, and by far this was my most positive moving experience. The team that came out were super funny and personable, and were also total bosses - they easily did things that the last movers said were impossible (removing door to apartment to get my ridiculously large couch out, for example). 5 stars is no exaggeration, would definitely book with them again. Super fair pricing as well.

Nash, came recommended for me, and Ive since recommended them to everyone I know for good reason. I cant say enough good things about Nash. Beyond their price (which was the best quote), I liked the fact that they actually hire the same team of movers (many of them were all childhood friends) rather than random daily paid labours people. It was huge to have movers I trusted. The blue plastic moving boxes were a game changer.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thanks for the review! We really appreciate it. Those blue boxes really are like cheating :D

reviews.review_text: Nash Moving took care of me through a local move from Burnaby to Richmond. They were wonderfully efficient, and were able to help make a stressful move much smoother. Everything arrived in perfect condition, from the massive steel bookshelves to the IKEA furniture! I wouldnt hesitate to use them again for another move.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Great to hear this. Thanks, Brittany!

reviews.review_text: We used Nash moving to move us out of our home of 29 years, first into their storage facility, and 5 months later, into our new condo. They were always reliable, were careful with all our furniture and belongings, and pleasant and courteous. We loved the blue boxes they supplied, used their services to pack our most fragile kitchen and dining room items, and   were very pleased in all aspects of both moves. Nate was very accommodating when we found out on short notice that we could book an elevator for our new place. While we paid for our storage monthly, the second part of the move to our new place was included in our original quote to move us once into the condo directly. The flexibility and full service options were perfect for our situation. Highly recommended.

After having a terrible moving experience with another company, we found Nash, and have since used them for 2 moves (yes we need to stop moving). Nash was professional with both moves, and gave us a fair quote. I have recommended them to all my friends!

Excellent communication all the way, and they wrapped up all of our valuables with padding and plastic wrap, including our couch, wardrobe, TV, paintings, etc. Our whole one-bedroom apartment was moved in a half-day and nothing was missing or damaged at all. We were very happy with Nate and his crew.

I found Nash on Facebook. I reached out to them for a quote and within a few days we had a video walk through a a quote. The guys were great. They were super professional. We had A LOT of stairs at the condo and no elevator...we didn t hear one complaint from anyone. They were quick and efficient and listening to a some great through backs. We would and have recommended Nash to friends.

Over all a great experience. Guys showed up on time. They were fast, efficient and professional. The men we dealt with were very friendly and polite and handled with care. They have a very professional booking system and get back to you very quickly. The price I had discussed over a video call conversation and there were zero hidden fees.  Ii would definitely put in trust this moving company with my stuff and highly recommend them!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Glad to have been of service, Carly!

reviews.review_text: We have used Nash Moving twice and both times they have been great! The have great customer service and are friendly and professional. They are always on time and very efficient. I would highly recommend them!

The service was professional from booking to moving day. The guys handled everything with care, and had all the right safety protocols in place to ensure to keep everyone healthy and safe! I highly recommend Nash Moving!
Nash Moving did a fantastic job on our move. Professional and well priced. I would use them again in a heartbeat and always recommend to friends.

These guys were awesome !! Super friendly and fun and know how to move efficiently. Moving can be stressful and hey made it easy! They were very careful with my stuff!! They wrapped everything Well and took their time to make sure nothing was damaged. They were great when they delivered they were kind enough to ask where I wanted everything. I would recommend them to anyone that wants an eco friendly way to move with a very fun crew!!

Aaron and Nate are rockstars!! Theyve helped me out twice so far, and definitely will again in the future. Ive never had anyone move anything of mine with such care and diligence. Their prices are also very, very fair. I cant say enough good things about them both!! Thanks again for moving my very heavy aquarium on such short notice. :)
Just had a very awesome moving experience with Nash Moving today, they arrived early and brought everything over carefully and rly professionally! Will recommend!

There arent enough words to describe how amazing they were. Right on time, respectful of my belongings and the building, kind and considerate, great price. What an amazing moving team! I highly recommend them! 10 out of 10. What a breath of fresh air in the moving industry.

When my wife and I moved in March during the pandemic the team was fantastic, they showed up on time 9am in Langley, loaded a 5 ton truck to the brim using their unique HEAVY DUTY blue packing tubs, carefully loaded our furniture and had it delivered and in our new condo in Burnaby by 3pm. The price was beyond fair and exactly what they quoted with NO HIDDEN Fees. I highly recommend this company, first rate service!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: So glad we could help! Thanks Nate!

reviews.review_text: If there was a 6th star as an option, Id immediately give it to NASH Moving! My husband and I HATE moving! (who doesnt?) But moving with NASH was the first time where we found ourselves ahead of schedule, drinking coffee (since we didnt need to help at all), and laughing. Seriously - the NASH team was having a good time and telling jokes, and my husband and I actually LAUGHED! Thats a huge testament to the difference with using NASH versus the other companies weve used in the past, where our stress levels were above maximum (and there was no sipping coffee or enjoying a good joke). I always recommend NASH and plan to never do another move without them. Theyre fun, fast, efficient and so strong that I dont have to worry about being helpful as a 52 person. They gave us moving containers in advance, disassembled all our furniture for us, and then reassembled it upon arrival. We were fully moved into our place and unpacked within a week, thanks to all the awesome help and perfect moving strategies. Thank you so much!!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: With 6 star customers it makes it that much easier! Thanks Jen!

reviews.review_text: Best moving team in the city. Ive worked with and along side these guys, I usually do repairs for movers, but Ive never had to fix anything for Nash because of the level of detail they put into each move.
Nash is my go to moving company every time. They are professional and always a pleasure to work with. 10/10 recommend!
Nate and his brother are great at what they do I was stuck when my bedroom flooded They picked my furniture and stored it for one week Great job guys! I highly recommend Nash Moving
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thanks Jerri! Glad we could help you!

reviews.review_text: Great group of guys! Everything went smoothly. The owners Nate and Aaron bent over backwards for us. They brought us more crates when we needed more. They accommodated us when we had to change our moving date last minute. If youre moving, hire these guys!

The best moving company we have ever dealt with! Employees were happy and very professional. Not only was ours a hard move, but the communication was excellent and the price was great. They were so helpful and did a fantastic job! Highly recommend this company.
Nothing but good things to say about Nash Moving. Were about to use them again and also referred our daughter to them as well. Hassle-free, on-time, professionals!

This company has the experience and service to handle the most demanding moves. Great team and super nice guys take great care of your most prized possessions. Finding such a service driven moving company was certainly a pleasant surprise. Thanks Nate!
Nash moving was so accommodating, helpful, flexible and very efficient!  Would highly recommend them to anyone! Will definitely use them on our next move!
Nash moving helped us with moving our office. Very accommodating, quick and efficient. Reasonably priced comparing to competitors and no hidden fees!

They are an amazing moving company that I have used for years.  Even my parents and friends have used them, and they provided excellent service every time.  Friendly and trustworthy.  I will be happy to use them for my next move!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: We do love referrals! Thank you, Michelle!

reviews.review_text: Nash showed up as promised. Did great and smooth job plus some extras in getting rid of donating items and stayed right on their quote. Will recommend them for sure.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: We guarantee our prices! Glad we could go that extra mile for you!

reviews.review_text: I used their move service. Very professional and hard working team. Their estimates were reasonable and  great work makes them leading service in Lower Mainland. I recommend this service to everyone. Thank you for providing excellent service. Keep it up.
We used Nash for a staging project and they were great. On time, professional and quick! It was a painless process. Will use them again.

These guys were good. Period. Everything you could want from your movers-very punctual, cordial and professional. They give you one rate and thats it--no truck fees, mileage fees,  etc. I would recommend all over again!
Nash moving has been excellent during my move which was bang in the middle of the pandemic. Nate and his team were fantastic!
The guys were fantastic! On time and very professional, they made sure my move was done fast and efficiently. Will definitely hire them again for my next move!
Moving is stressful at the best of times never mind during a pandemic! Nash moving made it a seamless process. Thank you !
reviews.response_from_owner_text: We are using the best safety protocols! Thank you Andrea!

reviews.review_text: Nash moved my family from our suite to new apartment.  Staff were friendly and personable and the move was done without damage.
These guys are real pros. Aaron and his team are the best moving company Ive ever had the pleasure of dealing with and I would highly recommend their services!
its one of a kind experience! they are so organized and the staff are very friendly. i just recently moved but so excited to re hire this guys on the next moving. love this people.
I highly recommend these movers! They were professional, and were extremely helpful with some very heavy, very challenging items. They made the move much easier and less stressful.

I cannot recommend this company highly enough. They have now handled two of our moves and gave outstanding service, going above and beyond in difficult circumstances. They are professional, personable, careful, and helpful.
A compete godsend for my last move. Professional, courteous and very friendly. Would recommend them and will definitely hire again for any move I need.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Cant wait to help you again, Jay!

reviews.review_text: Amazing company. Hired them for my move from Vancouver to Nanaimo and they were very friendly, fast and careful. Everything went great!
I highly recommend them. Their service is great, they are very responsible, honest and professional. They did two services for us and we couldn t be more happy with their job.
Excellent movers. Very careful service and fair pricing. Made my move so much easier.
They were excellent for our familys move! Accommodated our needs, were fast and clean! I recommend them highly!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thanks Adam! Was a pleasure to move you guys into your new place

reviews.review_text: Professional and organized.  Best mover we have ever hired, and we have hired many!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you, that means a lot to us!

reviews.review_text: Many thanks to Nate and Nathan for all their support!!
Excellent team. They respond quick and provide detailed information. I would say that this company is one to remember. Services: Vehicle transport
Great Movers, great people! Highly recommend them!
Great professional and friendly service will highly recommend them
I am impressed with their professionalism and efficiency.  Thanks
Reasonably priced, well organized, friendly and efficient.

Worked for these guys for a few months and the owner would literally pocket the tips the customers would give the employees.. Few things I didnt like about the way they moved like not using dollys enough or not having a ramp on the truck to move things easier in and out of the truck and the owner would just brush anything i said off like its nothing. Shady owners.. The other co workers I did moves with were rude and lazy. Would try to make me do most of the stairs and try to do the bare minimum to get away from doing real work. Would not recommend anyone work for this company. Beware!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Its hard to even justify this one with a response! You worked for us for one day and then no showed. Weve been in business for 10+ years and have had employees with us almost that long. They wouldnt stick with us if this was the case. Feel free to ask anyone of my movers what they think of the owners! 99% of them our our friends if not family at this point.
